Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.54,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,間もなく幕が上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.36,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再不情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.36,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,いやがおうでもな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.24,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.24,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,いいな
