Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.68,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,彌涼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.82,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本名是藤原弥凉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.82,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,本名は藤原彌涼
