Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.77,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,不准恶作剧哦  索多玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.77,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,悪戯しちゃだめだよ　ソドム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.72,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.72,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,おいで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.63,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.63,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,いい子だね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:38.46,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,十瑚酱  焰稚和愁生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:38.46,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,十瑚ちゃん 焰椎真君と愁生君は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.73,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这么说的话···
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.73,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ　そういえば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.04,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,愁生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.04,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,愁生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.40,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛先走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.40,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで先に行くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.12,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,难得一次也无妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.12,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,たまにはいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.76,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.76,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだよそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.08,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,夕月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.08,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,夕月
